abstract: >
  An automated AI agent designed to detect Broken Access Control (BAC) 
  vulnerabilities in REST APIs that implement Role-Based Access Control (RBAC). 
  This tool leverages Large Language Models (LLM) to perform intelligent and 
  comprehensive security testing, including BOLA, IDOR, Privilege Escalation, 
  and RBAC policy violations detection.
